Diep Thi Hoang, Olga Chernomor, Arndt von Haeseler, Bui Quang Minh,
and Le Sy Vinh (2017) UFBoot2: Improving the ultrafast bootstrap
approximation. Mol Biol Evol, in press.
https://doi.org/10.1093/molbev/msx281

